      "description": "Clean, good-condition car that presents well overall and should make a solid choice for someone wanting a nice driver without paying mint-condition money. The body, paint, and interior show well, with only the kind of light cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect from a properly used and maintained vehicle. It looks cared for, feels above average for its age, and should meet the expectations of a buyer looking for a dependable, well-kept example rather than a show car. Overall, this is a strong, honest vehicle with good curb appeal and no major visual red flags.",
