      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone seeking affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows clear signs of age and wear, but offers strong value at this price point for a buyer who prioritizes cost-conscious ownership. A straightforward option with room for improvement, priced to sell.",
